A photorealistic wide-angle photograph of the dramatic granite peaks of Mount Huashan in China shrouded in morning mist, with ancient stone steps carved into the steep cliff face winding upward through wisps of clouds, traditional wooden temple pavilions perched precariously on distant rocky outcrops, golden sunrise light breaking through the fog and illuminating the jagged mountain silhouettes, a sense of adventure and discovery permeating the scene, shot with dramatic depth and scale emphasizing the mountain's sacred majesty.
